This mod adds money, ec cards and automats to Minetest.

crafts:
**********
_____
|S|C| = Bankomat
-----
|S|G| = ec card
-----
|S|A| = Food Automat
-----
|S|B| = Tools Automat
-----
|S|I| = Ores Automat
-----
|S|1| = Money Automat
-----
S = Cobblestone
C = Coallump
G = Goldingot
A = Apple
B = Stoneaxe
I = Steelingot
1 = One currency

functions:
**********

Bankomat:

Pay in:
Put money in slot and click pay in.

Pay out:
Keep slot empty and click Get... .

Food-, Tools- and Ores Automat:
Klick with currency on top of the automat to pay in.
Put money into slot to pay in.
Put ec card into slot to pay with account of ec cards owner.
Klick button to pay item.
If enoug money item is added to Players inventory.

Money Automat:
Put ec card into slot to load money to ec cards owners account.
Klick Button to sell item.
Item is taken from Players inventory.
If ec card is in slot money is payed to owners account.
If no ec card is in slot money is added to players inventory.

Ec card:
Craft ec card to get ec card with is bound to your account of money2.
If you give ec card to friend, her can pay from your account(and pay in to your account).
Put ec card into automat to pay with ec card.

